---
interface Props {
  section: string;
  fallbackBody?: string;
}
const { section, fallbackBody } = Astro.props;
---

{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* CHALLENGES SECTION                                                  */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "challenges" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-4">
    Topstep offers a two-step evaluation process for futures traders to earn funding. Step one starts with the <strong>Trading Combine</strong>, then you move onto the <strong>Express Funded Account</strong>, then you'll receive a <strong>Live Funded Account</strong>.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Step 1 &mdash; Trading Combine</p>
      <p>Traders are evaluated in a simulated environment with specific profit and risk targets, paying a monthly fee based on account size.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Step 2 &mdash; Express Funded Account</p>
      <p>A simulated account where traders earn real profits. No monthly fee, but a $149 activation fee applies.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Live Funded Account</p>
      <p>Traders access real capital, with higher stakes. Breaching the maximum loss limit can result in closure of your live trading account.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mb-6">
    As with all prop challenges, the key to success in the Topstep trading program is managing risk effectively, hitting profit targets, and maintaining consistency.
  </p>

  <!-- ─── Overview Table ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Account Overview</h3>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-10">
    <table class="w-full text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
      <thead class="bg-slate-800 text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wide">
        <tr>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Account Size</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Trading Combine</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Express Funded Activation</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Profit Target</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Max Loss Limit</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$50K</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$49/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$149</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$3,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$2,000</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-slate-50">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$100K</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$99/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$149</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$6,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$3,000</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$150K</td>
