      Topstep offers a structured two-step process to earn funding, starting with the Trading Combine, where traders face realistic costs and recurring fees. The Express Funded Account requires a one-time activation fee, while the Live Funded Account offers real profits but has strict loss limits. The consistency target and scaling plan promote disciplined trading, and the unlimited time limit on the Combine gives traders the flexibility to progress at their own pace.
