{/* SPREADS / COMMISSION FEES AND PRICING SECTION                       */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "spreads" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-3">
    Unlike many other prop firms, Topstep exclusively operates within the <strong>futures markets</strong>, meaning there are no spreads when trading the available products.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-6">
    However, multiple layers of commissions and fees apply, and these vary based on the platform, exchange, and stage of the challenge you are at.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Step 1 Fees: Trading Combine</p>
      <p>Monthly challenge fee + per-trade fees (commission, clearing, and exchange fees) + potential platform subscription costs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Step 2 Fees: Express Funded</p>
      <p>One-time activation fee + per-trade fees + potential platform subscription costs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Step 3 Fees: Live Funded</p>
      <p>Monthly exchange data fees, platform subscription costs (if applicable), and additional fees for advanced data (like Level 2 Depth of Market).</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Additionally, if you violate any of the rules during the challenge phases, you will need to reset your account. The reset fees are <strong>$49</strong> for a $50K account, <strong>$99</strong> for a $100K account, and <strong>$149</strong> for a $150K account.
  </p>

  <!-- ─── Stage 1: Trading Combine Fees ────────────────────────────── -->
